formatted_items.arguments:
{"to":["emily.thompson@apexsolutions.com"],"subject":"Re: A quick overview of the people I spend time with","body":"Hi Emily,

Thanks for reaching out! I’m happy to give you a snapshot of the circles I’m most often connected with right now:

• Work teammates – I stay in close contact with our marketing colleagues. We collaborate on projects and often catch up outside of meetings as well.

• Volunteer crew – I’m involved with a local community-service group that runs weekend events. It’s a great chance to meet people who care about giving back.

• Long-time friends – I still keep in touch with a handful of classmates from university. We get together whenever our schedules line up and keep a group chat running in between.

That about covers the main groups I regularly spend time with. Let me know if you were curious about anything more specific or if you’d like an introduction to anyone.

Hope this helps!

Best,
[Your Name]"}
